  <body>
    <div class="content">
      <div id="intro">
        <p>Develop as an apprentice, in your own way!</p>
        <div id="buttons">
          <a id="login" href="/auth/google">Login</a>
          <a id="signup" href="/auth/google">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="page_summary">
        <div class="image">
          <img
            id="laptop_image"
            src="/images/laptop.png"
            alt="Laptop With Code"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="main_header">
          Everything you need to become a successful Apprentice
        </p>
        <p class="headers">
          Challenge yourself with quizzes and find useful resources that are
          tailored to you!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="display">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column">
            <h4>What?</h4>
            <p>
              For Apprentices By Apprentices... We want to allow users to share
              resources that were helpful to them, and also have the freedom to
              share their own work and knowledge to gain credibility or to
              simply help others.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <h4>Why?</h4>
            <p>
              We aspire to share our knowledge and experience to upcoming
              apprentices to ensure they have the same or even better experience
              that we had.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <img
              id="collab_img"
              src="/images/graphic.png"
              alt="Collaboration"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
